FOR 1.0.0:
rewrite lag compensation / main loop
	(reduce lag problems - m_stepFault is one possible cause)
	(is not sent via the network)
	but i think it should be low ?
	on the other hand it could accumulate up to stepsize
	=> in the moment ~0.02 sec - which is quite much
- reduce text on startup (perhaps print text faster (glterminal))

DEBIAN:
	split server and client into seperate packages (where to put the bot ?)
DOPE: add a protocol handling byte order issues


